<title>ḥbtny mḥbẗ ạ̉bdyẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ḥbtny mḥbẗ ạ̉bdyẗ qdmt ḥyạtk
 yạ fạdy mạdd ly ạ̹ydyk bạlḥryẗ dy mḥbẗ ʿẓymẗ mḥbẗ ạ̉b ạlqrạr- ḥbk ạ̉srny yạ ḥbyb wmʿzyny wạ̉nạ gẖryb kmlt ḥbk bạlṣlyb ḥbk ʿjyb 2- bmḥbẗ dʿytny lạ̉ḥḍạnk wwʿdt tʿysẖny slạmk wfy qlb ạlkẖwf sẖwft ḥnạnk dy mḥbẗ ʿẓymẗ mḥbẗ
 ạ̉b 3- wfy zmn ạlḥb ạ̉nạ jạy ạ̹lyk jạy ạ̉twb ʿnd
 rjlyk tḥyạ fy ạlḥb ḥbk yạ mlyk dy mḥbẗ ʿẓymẗ mḥbẗ
 ạ̉b</lyrics>
</song>